Package: pkgsite
Title: Convert the Reference Pages into Quarto Files
Version: 0.0.0.9004
Authors@R: c(
    person("Edgar", "Ruiz", , "edgar@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"),
           comment = c(ROR = "03wc8by49"))
  )
Description: Makes it easier to create a Quarto website for your R
    package.  It converts the Rd documents into Quarto documents
    individually.
